      "language": "Python",
      "code": "```python\nimport termios, typing\n\ndef get_keypress():\n    fd = sys.stdin.fileno()\n    old = termios.tcgetattr(fd)\n    try:\n        termios.tcflush(fd, termios.TCFLUSH)\n        char = sys.stdin.read(1) \n    finally:\n        termios.tcsetattr(fd, termios.TCSADRAIN, old)\n    return char\n\ndef main():\n    while True:\n        key = get_keypress()\n        # Process the input here...\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    main()\n```"
    }
